package.name: handlebars
package.description: This extension embeds a Handlebars interpreter into PHP, allowing the execution of Handlebars templates.
package.notes: - Fixed test failure on PHP 8 (@remicollet) - Fixed test failure on 32bit - The compiled template produced by `Handlebars\VM::compile()` should now be deterministic, if using handlebars.c >= 0.7.1.
